PhenolicsDB: PhenolicsDB: phenolics MS/MS (LC-ESI-QTOF) database repository

Source: R/PhenolicsDB-package.R
PhenolicsDB-package.Rd

Raw MS/MS data of a set of authentic phenolics standards, including phenolic acids, flavonoids, dihydrochalcones, and carbohydrates. MS/MS data was collected using an Agilent QTOF 6545 and a 6546, in negative and positive polarities, and 20 and 40 eV (CE). The raw MS/MS files will be used jointly with the MS2extract package to create in-house MS/MS libraries.
